{
  "texts": [
    "https://github.com/huggingface/transformers",
    "For consistency, our storage footprint calculations are based only on the size of model files (*.safetensors), including the adapter of QLoRA models.",
    "We exclude the tokenizer and configuration files, as their contribution to the overall size is relatively small (∼ 13 MB) and they are unaffected by our optimization methods.",
    "All sizes are computed using the decimal definition of gigabytes, where 1 GB = 1000 3 bytes.",
    "To achieve these compression gains from layer pruning, the Qwen2-Audio model must initially be loaded in bfloat16 data type."
  ]
}